product.name: Magnetic Wireless Charger iPhone,6FT Charger for Apple MagSafe Charger 2Pack Fast Wireless Charging Pad for iPhone 16 Pro Max/16 Pro/16 Plus/15 ProMax/15/14/13/12/AirPods 3/2/Pro Mag-Safe Charging Pad
product.description: Safe and Reliable: Intelligent chips can promote smooth output of current, prevent overcurrent, overvoltage and overheating.The ultra-thin design can effectively dissipate heat during the charging process, ensuring safe charging.You can rest assured that your device will be protected during the charging process. 15W Fast Magsafe Charger: When charging iPhone 16 with a 15W magnetic charger, it only takes half an hour to go from 0-50% and 2.5 hours to go from 0-100%, which is three times faster than the original 5W charging speed, providing you with a more efficient life. Protable Design Easy to Carry: Buying ultra-thin magnetic chargers really makes your life easier. Its slim design is very suitable for mobile charging. The 6-foot hard wired cable charger and 20W PD adapter are perfect for home, office, or travel. 2-Pack Advantages: You can use one to charge your phone and the other to charge your AirPods, or share with family and friends without plugging or unplugging the charging cable. Universal Compatibility: -iPhone 16/16e/16 Plus/16 Pro Max/16 Pro -iPhone 15/15 Plus/15 Pro Max/15 Pro -iPhone 14/14 Pro/14 Pro Max/14 Plus -iPhone 13/13 Mini/13 Pro/13 Pro Max -iPhone 12/12 Mini/12 Pro/12 Pro Max -iPhone 11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max -iPhone X/XR/XS/XS Max -iPhone 8/8 Plus -AirPods（with wireless charging case） What You Get: 2 * 15W 6ft Magnetic Charger for iPhone 2 * 20W PD USB C Wall Charger Adapter
product.bullet_points:
• 15W Fast Magnetic Charger:Our 15W magnetic wireless charger comes with a 20W power adapter for fast charging.Charge iPhone 16 from 0 to 100% within 2-2.5 hours.You can easily and quickly power on the device.The magnetic design provides a stable and comfortable fit, without sliding or falling off, making charging more convenient and reassuring
• Wide Compatibility:Adopting the latest upgraded magnetic technology, it is perfectly compatible with iPhone 16/16e/16 Plus/16 Pro/16 Pro Max/15/15 Pro/15 Plus/15 Pro Max 14/14 Pro/14 Pro Max/13 Pro/13 Pro Max/13 mini/12/12 Pro/12 Pro Max/12 mini AirPods 3/2/Pro, and also supports iPhone 8 and above models (requires Mag-Safe protective case)
• Strong Magnetic Suction:Equipped with a high-strength magnetic attraction module, the charging pad can automatically and accurately align with the charging area, allowing for instant charging without dropping, making wireless charging more efficient and stable.When charging, there is no need to use the phone interface, and it supports 360° charging angle adjustment, allowing for the most comfortable charging method to be adjusted at any time
• Intelligent Safety Protection:The wireless charger is equipped with an intelligent chip that provides overcurrent, overvoltage and overheating protection.Advanced low-temperature charging technology ensures that the device does not overheat or damage the battery during long-term charging, making each charge safer and more reliable.Whether charging at night or using for a long time, you can enjoy an efficient and stable wireless fast charging experience with peace of mind
• What You Get:2 Pack 20W USB C wall adapter and 2 Pack 15W 6ft magnetic wireless charging cable, If there are any questions during the charging process of the product, please contact customer service and we will reply within 24 hours
